Global Variable# NSMetadataItemDisplayNameKey

iOS 5.0+iPadOS 5.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.7+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataItemDisplayNameKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataItemDisplayNameKey#Discussion)

The value is an [`NSString`](/documentation/foundation/nsstring) object with the display name of the item, which may be different then the file system name.
